Description: TTL LCD system monitor for Thermaltake Tower 200 and compatible USB LCD panels
 A modern C++ utility for driving 3.9-inch USB LCD panels (480x128) with
 live system monitoring, custom TTF fonts, bar graphs, and JSON config.
